{"type": "article", "id": 29508, "title": "晶莹剔透的树脂桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-12T23:01:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712221518SJ3iGnXOPDpkEd1w.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>韩国设计师 <a href=\"http://saeromyoon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saerom Yoon</a> 最近设计了一个名为 Crystal 的家具系列，包含两张漂亮的T 字型树脂桌。Yoon 将颜料直接加入了树脂中，打造出了梦幻般的渐变效果。使用的两种颜色也很容易让人联想到潘通的 2016 年<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/18813.html\">“年度流行色”</a>，粉晶色和静谧蓝的融合色。线条分明的造型搭配淡雅的渐变色使最后的成品看起来非常精致，如同水晶一般晶莹剔透。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712221534PNoZ4XRMUTmGdJ98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712221535Xz2KWqSwIH8smUMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712221534x6icUkNLljo7EZ8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712221535fWgzmD7Sqr6GcdkH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}